Hi! I'm Jacob Lovins and I'm a full stack developer with creative problem solving experience educated at Point University and Georgia Tech, focused on full stack web technologies. I have developed skills in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Node.js, Express, MySQL, MongoDB, React, and full stack responsive web design. My strengths include communication, organization, discipline, leadership, following documentation and protocol, and collaboration. I’ve lead many teams on projects and events and have experience in servers and handling multiple internet devices. I recently finished a team project where I integrated multiple API’s, voice, and facial expression recognition.

I’m passionate about designing and integrating features and learning the newest and most interesting technologies in the tech field. I love sorting through problems and finding unique solutions. I’m excited to build projects with new and innovative technologies and to be in an environment that has great developers that challenge me to become the best I can be.
